{"tid":255331,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【真窮人恩物】618呎賣200萬平絕私樓　「張保仔」沽澄碧邨竟賺一球","createTime":"2017-05-23T23:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T00:32:37.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e52789b234c16cf6e33fd18b79fecd84677eabb","tid":255331,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495549263_67d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495549263_67d0.jpg&h=9f9f51a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大嶼山澄碧邨交通惡劣，島上亦無設施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495549266_505e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495549266_505e.jpg&h=81613755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澄碧邨渡輪屬住客專屬服務，只准住客及獲批准人士乘搭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495549268_c89c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495549268_c89c.jpg&h=d80096e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本報記者曾於2015年採訪澄碧邨，當時會所已變廢墟，並驚現狗屍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495549273_f2cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495549273_f2cd.jpg&h=290a364a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495549276_cd22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495549276_cd22.jpg&h=07187060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495549348_eec9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495549348_eec9.gif&h=6e82ebb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本報早前報導大嶼山澄碧邨兩個單位將於本周四拍賣，實用面積1,240方呎，開價225萬元，呎價1,815元，被視為全港最平上車盤，迅即熱爆全城。<br />\n<br />\n這個隱世荒島，雖然網民形容為「鬼屋」，甚至話呢度「好X隔涉架，同未開發無分別，出意外無人救到你」，屋苑會所更荒廢驚見狗屍，但樓市瘋狂，「鬼屋」又如何，一樣都有得炒。有長洲炒家3年前僅以100萬元低撈澄碧邨，剛以200萬元轉手勁賺「1球」。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，澄碧邨1期11座地下單號A室，本月18日登記以200萬元易手。單位實用面積618方呎，呎價3,236元，幾可肯定平絕全港私樓。<br />\n<br />\n至於邊個咁有眼光，人棄我取，我不入地獄誰入地獄。賣出單位買家為蘇禮安，據知他在長洲經營餐廳「張保仔館」，2014年3月僅以100萬元買入，並毋須銀行按揭，「full pay」現金買孤島，持有單位滿3年「SSD」鬆綁後隨即沽貨，賬面獲利100萬元，升幅1倍更跑贏大市，中原城市領先指數同期升幅只約三成。新買家則姓黃。<br />\n<br />\n至於以100萬元將單位賣給蘇禮安的人姓陳，即再上一手業主，1989年買入樓價為30萬元。<br />\n<br />\n澄碧邨是和記地產（八十年代合併為和黃）七十年代中期進軍地產的首批項目，發展原意是「大班屋」，全邨220伙，2014年本報有記者採訪，據悉當時僅數十個有人居住，當時直擊會所變成廢墟(見另文， <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pSPKOP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pSPKOP&d=10lXKAqoaEf1JWXJ5ZYNmS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9f879f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pSPKOP</a> )。<br />\n<br />\n澄碧邨位於香港大嶼山芝麻灣半島，交通惡劣，沒有道路連接出入香港市區，依靠渡輪往來長洲，船程約15分鐘。島上無設施，任何民生用品都要坐船到長洲。但渡輪屬住客專屬服務，只准住客及獲批准人士乘搭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56733371&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56733371%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&d=10lXKAqoaEf1JWXJ5ZYNmS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=ccbdbebe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56733371%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&h=0360cb87\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56733371&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524</a>"},{"pid":"e3d286b312352828e916234ff1d852b71b45a951","tid":255331,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:20:14.000Z","msg":"條狗屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fde0c15fdd6a73eb378fd16edb5a5f542564c1","tid":255331,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條狗屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應係係冇咗玻璃之後入咗去然後餓死"},{"pid":"8be24503ff29c0bba4210c1285379e60920693c0","tid":255331,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:26:11.000Z","msg":"發展成渡假村可能有得諗，不過投入資本可觀，要開條陸路"},{"pid":"636d0f5022d9080d86626539689871014726a21e","tid":255331,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:27:57.000Z","msg":"FALLOUT4"},{"pid":"05188c1be80d9b7f87e23e5418187f92ae50356e","tid":255331,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發展成渡假村可能有得諗，不過投入資本可觀，要開條陸路</blockquote><br />\n巴打又準備入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7861e468da3ed886e2cf5489119515100de406d9","tid":255331,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>發展成渡假村可能有得諗，不過投入資本可觀，要開條陸路</blockquote><br />\n巴打又準備入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咁嘅財力仲喺連登咩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d61a7f4ba5c53350245820a3e4dce80bd8cba3","tid":255331,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>發展成渡假村可能有得諗，不過投入資本可觀，要開條陸路</blockquote><br />\n巴打又準備入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咁嘅財力仲喺連登咩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過果度要裝修都唔知點搞&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46936089789c01a10e8aa606779072660167534e","tid":255331,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:24:42.000Z","msg":"上車恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43eb00d74b1d3d3f4efa88c1571e09f32cf3c511","tid":255331,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:29:20.000Z","msg":"個渡輪未蝕錢？"},{"pid":"1cc0ddbefe0b0a2c8e7467de3745d4390820d8e5","tid":255331,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個渡輪未蝕錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能長洲啲街渡兼埋，東坪洲以前一星期都有一班來回渡輪，星期六去，星期日返，只有一班，唔記得係邊個島渡輪兼埋行一行嗰度"}]}